    {
      "title": "Beacon Crossing",
      "lines": [
        "Four beacons ring the flats, two to a bank, and the channel cuts between them.",
        "Keep any three burning at dawn. The far pair only relights if you cross under fire.",
        "Brine-hulks chew the barricades on the bridge — repair, or lose the span."
      ],
